OL,3,C400,000 households in Wales estimated
OL,4,Cto be hit by Winter Fuel payment cuts
OL,6,FAn estimated 400,000 households in
OL,7,FWales are expected to be impacted by
OL,8,Fcuts to the Winter Fuel Allowance, the
OL,9,FUK government has confirmed.
OL,11,FThe Chancellor has defended the move
OL,12,Fto scrap the payments for some
OL,13,Fpensioners insisting it will be offset
OL,14,Fby increases by pensions and lower
OL,15,Fenergy prices this winter compared to
OL,16,Flast year.
