OL,3,C400,000 households in Wales estimated
OL,4,Cto be hit by Winter Fuel payment cuts
OL,6,FBut Rachel Reeves and Prime Minister
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer have faced criticism
OL,8,Ffrom opponents, campaigners and some
OL,9,Fof their own MPs over the decision to
OL,10,Fmeans test winter fuel payments.
OL,12,FPeople who do not receive pension
OL,13,Fcredits or other benefits will no
OL,14,Flonger be eligible for the allowance,
OL,15,Fwhich is worth up to #300.
