OL,3,C400,000 households in Wales estimated
OL,4,Cto be hit by Winter Fuel payment cuts
OL,6,FReplying to a question from Plaid
OL,7,FCymru MP, Ann Davies, the government
OL,8,Fconfirmed that they had calculated the
OL,9,Fnumber of Welsh households affected
OL,10,Fbased on the number of those who
OL,11,Fcurrently receive pension credit.
OL,13,FIn a statement, the Department for
OL,14,FWork and Pensions said the estimation
OL,15,Fof 400,000 households did not take
OL,16,Finto account any potential increase in
OL,17,Fthe number of people that apply for
OL,18,Fpension credit, which may happen as a
OL,19,Fresult of the policy.
