OL,3,C400,000 households in Wales estimated
OL,4,Cto be hit by Winter Fuel payment cuts
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's Ms Davies described the
OL,7,Frevelation as "shocking", saying,
OL,8,F"Pensioners are being pushed deeper
OL,9,Finto fuel poverty, unfairly
OL,10,Fscapegoated by Rachel Reeves to
OL,11,Fpromote a pro-austerity narrative that
OL,12,Fwill have serious consequences for
OL,13,Folder people.
OL,15,F"Even if we accept Labour's argument
OL,16,Fthat pensioners don't need this
OL,17,Fsupport due to rising pensioner
OL,18,Fincomes, are they really suggesting
OL,19,Fthat 400,000 households in Wales are
OL,20,Fwell-off and can manage without
OL,21,Fsupport this winter?
