OL,6,F"Anyone with any understanding of
OL,7,FWelsh communities will know that
OL,8,Fnotion is absurd", she added.
OL,10,FA UK Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,11,Fare absolutely committed to supporting
OL,12,Fpensioners and giving them the dignity
OL,13,Fand security they deserve in
OL,14,Fretirement.
OL,16,F"That's why, through our commitment to
OL,17,Fprotect the triple lock, over 12
OL,18,Fmillion pensioners could see their
OL,19,Fstate pension increase by almost a
OL,20,Fthousand pounds over the next five
OL,21,Fyears.
